message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with signal processing and audio signals. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (speech processing), cs.LG (machine learning), cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses convolutional architectures and neural networks. Finally, cs.SY (systems and control) could also be a possible category as the paper proposes a framework for enhancing perceived acoustical quality.
